reviewText:
Rocket League is an overall excelent game:
+Competitive;
+Awesome Visuals;
+Acessible to new players;
+5 min, non-stop competitive play;
+hats;

-Should have some kind of radar;
-Some maps are more laggy then others
-Not enough hats;


9/10 highly recomended

